 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.5.9","title":"task(opentui-import parity tests): E2E gap-closure regression suite with detailed migration logs","description":"Objective: Implement end-to-end suite that re-runs previously blocked fixtures after parity changes and verifies automatic closure of targeted gaps.\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n1. Suite tracks before/after gap counts and affected fixtures.\n2. Logs include gap IDs, applied capability paths, and certification impact.\n3. CI gate fails if closed gaps regress in subsequent runs.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:33:48.521171630Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:13.122140638Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","feature-parity","opentui-import","test"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.1.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:13.122083491Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.10","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:44.061866678Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.5","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:33:48.521171630Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:44.668635425Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.5.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:45.123579558Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.6","title":"epic(opentui-import): Validation, certification, and confidence scoring","description":"## Background
Provide certification-grade proof that translated FrankenTUI outputs preserve semantics and improve quality where allowed by contract.

## Scope
- Baseline harnesses, trace capture/replay, and differential comparators (semantic/visual/perf/accessibility).
- Determinism soak, fuzz/adversarial scenarios, and verdict policy engine.
- Machine-checkable proof artifacts for semantic-preservation obligations.
- Unit + E2E certification pipelines with full evidence ledgers and replay diagnostics.

## Success Criteria
1. Certification verdicts are reproducible and traceable to comparator evidence and contract clauses.
2. Proof artifacts and witness integrity checks pass for required preservation obligations.
3. Determinism soak/fuzz pipelines surface divergences with minimized replayable counterexamples.
4. CI-ready E2E gates block release when certification thresholds are not met.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:28:21.390109139Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T22:22:56.668811746Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["certification","opentui-import","verification"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.6","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:28:21.390109139Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
